metadata.name: Sad Pepe
metadata.description:
Pepe, oh Pepe, where did you go?  
Missing the green days, the profits that flow.  
You thought you were a genius, a crypto king,  
But now you're just another hodler, holding nothing.

Your portfolio's crashed, your coins are dead,  
The bull run's over, it's all in your head.  
You remember the hype, the fomo so real,  
But now it's just regret, and a bitter pill to feel.

You miss the days of Lambos and moon,  
The feeling of winning, so bright like a boon.  
But now you're broke, your bank account in the red,  
And you wish you had listened to what everyone said.

Oh Pepe, don't worry, it's just a game,  
Crypto's a rollercoaster, it's never the same.  
Hold on tight, and keep your head up high,  
And soon the green days will return, and you'll fly.

Oh Pepe, don't lose hope, don't give up the fight,  
The market may be down, but it will take flight.  
Your fortunes will rise, your investments will soar,  
And the green days will come back, just like before.
